-- Richemont Says Rupert to Step Down From CEO Role March 31
-- B y   D e r m o t   D o h e r t y
-- 2012-11-09T06:05:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-09/richemont-says-rupert-to-step-down-from-ceo-role-march-31.html
Cie. Financiere Richemont SA (CFR)  said
Bernard Fornas and Richard Lepeu will become joint chief
executive officers from April, replacing Johann Rupert who will
step down from the role.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
